{"tid":2229709,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2017年 奧巴馬授予拜登自由勳章 拜登感動落淚","createTime":"2020-10-04T14:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T14:49:24.000Z","uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"248d3f0a70dca440c4e4600e82943828fc5b9241","tid":2229709,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"仆你個街好心民主黨唔好推拜登去選啦 <br />\n都一把年紀 要人臨老唔過得世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SzBFR2EE8hM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSzBFR2EE8hM&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil6%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=3c155bd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SzBFR2EE8hM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/179B6/production/_93549669_hi037240027.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F800%2Fcpsprodpb%2F179B6%2Fproduction%2F_93549669_hi037240027.jpg&h=a8587012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統奧巴馬在當地時間星期四（1月12日）向一臉意外但熱淚盈眶的副總統拜登授予總統自由勳章。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統奧巴馬在當地時間星期四（1月12日）向一臉意外但熱淚盈眶的副總統拜登授予總統自由勳章。這是由美國總統授予的最高平民榮譽。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬稱讚說，拜登副總統因其&quot;對美國同胞的信任、對國家的熱愛和一生的服務&quot;而獲頒勳章。<br />\n<br />\n頒獎之際，奧巴馬總統和拜登副總統即將卸任，而候任總統特朗普將於1月20日宣誓就職美國總統。<br />\n<br />\n拜登表示，他計劃在卸任後繼續積極參與民主黨的政治事務。<br />\n<br />\n拜登在頒發勳章的儀式上說，未曾想過能獲得這份殊榮。<br />\n<br />\n拜登說：「總統先生，我感謝你，感謝你的友誼，感謝你的家人。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/1DFA/production/_93547670_037239886-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F800%2Fcpsprodpb%2F1DFA%2Fproduction%2F_93547670_037239886-1.jpg&h=a9418c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n什麼是總統自由勳章？<br />\n總統自由勳章是由美國總統授予的最高平民榮譽。<br />\n 1963年由肯尼迪總統設立，取代之前的自由獎章。<br />\n授予範圍：&quot;對美國國家安全、國家利益和世界和平、文化或其他重要的公共或私人領域作出傑出貢獻者&quot;。<br />\n主要獲頒者類別：政治; 商業; 軍事; 音樂; 電影; 新聞。<br />\n兩次獲頒者：科林&middot;鮑威爾（Colin Powell）和埃爾斯沃思&middot;邦克（Ellsworth Bunker）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-38606235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-38606235&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil6%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=ba8c35f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-38606235&h=61fcf62d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-38606235</a>"},{"pid":"1de37ab86f7d33a33aef90f7bf4adbb6dbfb872a","tid":2229709,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:47:18.000Z","msg":"47 years of failure"},{"pid":"5ac175d572cdbc06d2432cbd7401253c23887f7e","tid":2229709,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1de37ab86f7d33a33aef90f7bf4adbb6dbfb872a","tid":2229709,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:47:18.000Z","msg":"47 years of failure"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96958c92940e6a40b579c4aaa42289a109742677","tid":2229709,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1de37ab86f7d33a33aef90f7bf4adbb6dbfb872a","tid":2229709,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20